OL,7,FAristocrat Constance Marten posed as a
OL,8,Ffreelance journalist called Caroline
OL,9,Fas she concealed her tragic newborn
OL,10,Fbaby, a court has heard.
OL,12,FMarten, 37, and her partner Mark
OL,13,FGordon, 50, are on trial at the Old
OL,14,FBailey over the death of baby Victoria
OL,15,Fwhile on the run from authorities in
OL,16,FJanuary 2023.
