OL,3,CConstance Marten posed as journalist
OL,4,Cas she hid tragic newborn baby, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe baby was thought to have been born
OL,8,Fat a Cumbria cottage in late December
OL,9,F2022, and the couple allegedly kept
OL,10,Fher secret to prevent her from being
OL,11,Ftaken into care ` as their four other
OL,12,Fchildren had been.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, jurors heard a statement
OL,15,Ffrom hotel receptionist Cathy Lloyd,
OL,16,Fwho interacted with Marten when she
OL,17,Fchecked into the Ibis Hotel at Lymm
OL,18,FServices in Warrington at 4am on
OL,19,FJanuary 4 2023.
