OL,7,FIn her statement, Ms Lloyd said Marten
OL,8,Fhad given her name as Caroline Marten
OL,9,Fand told her she was a freelance
OL,10,Fjournalist.
OL,12,FShe said the defendant had seemed
OL,13,F"extremely well-spoken" and "genuine",
OL,14,Fbut "very tired".
OL,16,FThe witness said: "Constance made
OL,17,Fconversation with me and was very
OL,18,Fsweet and conversational.
