OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"She told me she was very tired after
OL,8,Fdriving 'a hell of a long way'. She
OL,9,Ftold me she had lost her credit card
OL,10,Fand if she could pay cash. She told me
OL,11,Fshe lived in Hackney and just wanted
OL,12,Fto go home."
OL,14,FHaving told her she was a freelance
OL,15,Fjournalist, Marten chatted with Ms
OL,16,FLloyd about publicity for her brother
OL,17,Fwho was in a play, jurors heard.
