OL,7,FMs Lloyd said in her statement that
OL,8,Fshe handed over her email address and
OL,9,Fphone number, but never heard back
OL,10,Ffrom Marten.
OL,12,FShe told how Gordon entered reception
OL,13,Fshortly after Marten had gone to her
OL,14,Froom.
OL,16,FHe appeared to be "very moody" and did
OL,17,Fnot reply to her inquiry about whether
OL,18,Fhe had checked in, which she found
OL,19,F"unnerving", jurors heard.
