OL,7,FShe said Marten had seemed "so normal"
OL,8,Fand "really sweet" as they chatted
OL,9,Fagain about her brother's play,
OL,10,Faccording to her statement read by
OL,11,Fprosecutor Joel Smith KC.
OL,13,FMs Lloyd said: "I really thought she
OL,14,Fwas a journalist. At no time did I see
OL,15,FConstance and Mark together. At no
OL,16,Fpoint did I see a baby with either of
OL,17,Fthem.
