OL,7,F"I definitely did not see a baby or
OL,8,Fany baby items, None of their body
OL,9,Flanguage indicated they had a baby
OL,10,Fwith them."
OL,12,FThe prosecution has alleged that the
OL,13,Fcouple failed to provide for their
OL,14,Fbaby properly and carried her in a
OL,15,Fshopping bag-for-life or underneath
OL,16,FMarten's coat during her short life.
OL,18,FJurors have heard that Marten was a
OL,19,Fwealthy woman with access to funds to
OL,20,Fbuy whatever was needed.
