OL,7,FThe day before Marten and Gordon
OL,8,Fchecked into the Ibis Hotel, she had
OL,9,Freceived #3,400 into her bank account
OL,10,Ffrom a trust fund, the court was told.
OL,12,FOn January 5 2023, the couple
OL,13,Fabandoned their belongings on the M61
OL,14,Fmotorway near Bolton, Greater
OL,15,FManchester, after their Peugeot car
OL,16,Fburst into flames.
OL,18,FKen Hudson filmed the fire on the
OL,19,Fmotorway and called emergency services
OL,20,Fat 6.19pm.
