OL,7,FHe told jurors that he saw a female
OL,8,Fpassenger holding a bundle with a
OL,9,Fbaby's head with wispy hair showing.
OL,11,FGiving evidence in court, Mr Hudson
OL,12,Fsaid he had asked her "is the baby
OL,13,Falright", and she replied: "She's
OL,14,Ffine."
OL,16,FHe touched the baby's head and said
OL,17,F"God bless", he said.
OL,19,FMr Hudson explained: "I'm a Christian
OL,20,Fman, have been all my life...It's what
OL,21,FI've always done."
