OL,7,FPolice launched a search for the
OL,8,Fmissing baby after a placenta was
OL,9,Ffound in the wreckage.
OL,11,FThe defendants travelled across
OL,12,FEngland in taxis and ended up on the
OL,13,FSouth Downs where the baby died while
OL,14,Fthey lived "off grid" in a tent.
OL,16,FThe prosecution has alleged that baby
OL,17,FVictoria died from hypothermia or was
OL,18,Fsmothered while co-sleeping in the
OL,19,F"flimsy" tent, despite past warnings.
