OL,7,FThe child's body was discovered with
OL,8,Frubbish inside a shopping bag-for-life
OL,9,Fin a disused shed near Brighton
OL,10,Ffollowing the defendants' arrests on
OL,11,FFebruary 27 2023.
OL,13,FMarten and Gordon, of no fixed
OL,14,Faddress, have denied the gross
OL,15,Fnegligence manslaughter of their
OL,16,Fdaughter Victoria and causing or
OL,17,Fallowing her death between January 4
OL,18,Fand February 27 2023.
